Ann May https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ann_May 0 Ann May (1901 – July 26, 1985) was a silent film star who made motion pictures from (1919–1925). Her given name was Anna Max and she was born in Cincinnati, Ohio. In appearance she was compared to Dorothy Gish, with her short fluffy hair and eyes which sparkled.
